# Optional: Vercel auto-rotation support
# FreshBooks rotates refresh tokens on each use. To auto-persist the new token:
#   VERCEL_API_TOKEN=<Vercel token with "Edit Project" scope>
#   VERCEL_PROJECT_ID=<project ID from Vercel dashboard>
#   VERCEL_REFRESH_ENV_ID=<env var ID for FRESHBOOKS_REFRESH_TOKEN, from Vercel env vars API>
# Without these, update FRESHBOOKS_REFRESH_TOKEN manually after each rotation.

# To re-authorize FreshBooks (e.g. after token loss):
#   1. Set FRESHBOOKS_CLIENT_ID + FRESHBOOKS_CLIENT_SECRET in Vercel
#   2. Visit https://youneedled.com/api/auth/freshbooks-start
#   3. Authorize in FreshBooks → copy the FRESHBOOKS_REFRESH_TOKEN shown
#   4. Add it to Vercel env vars and redeploy
